    • Method Detail

      • fields

        public static Compute.NetworkOption fields(Compute.NetworkField... fields)
        Returns an option to specify the network's fields to be returned by the RPC call. If this option is not provided, all network's fields are returned. NetworkOption.fields can be used to specify only the fields of interest. NetworkInfo.getNetworkId() and NetworkInfo.getConfiguration() are always returned, even if not specified.
